16:10.769 --> 16:13.237
which makes it extremely difficult
to treat with antibiotics.

16:13.339 --> 16:17.007
It basically learns how not
to be affected by the drugs.

16:17.109 --> 16:20.677
Stephanie's banking basically
her entire intestinal health

16:20.779 --> 16:25.850
on this procedure, which took all
of, I feel like eight minutes.

16:25.952 --> 16:27.513
So it's strange,
but this could be the...

16:27.586 --> 16:30.520
basically the new
frontier of medicine.

16:30.622 --> 16:31.722
People's shit.

16:31.824 --> 16:33.924
Morton:
<i>Before a transplant,</i>

16:34.026 --> 16:35.466
<i>Stephanie's colon
had been taken over</i>

16:35.494 --> 16:37.661
<i>by C. Diff bacteria,
causing her frequent</i>

16:37.763 --> 16:40.231
<i>and painful diarrhea, and
